CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: The Beachbody Co Inc is a holding company involved in offering both streamed and live fitness and nutrition programs as well as various products. The company operates through two core business platforms - Beachbody and Openfit. It earns the majority of the revenue from the United States. The company operates and manages its business in two operating segments, Beachbody and Other.
